node.text: Welcome to the launch of the all new 2022 @cyclesdevinci Spartan enduro mountain bike! Watch now as @neildonoghue and @doddstar1979 check out all the details before taking it for a ride on the rough and fast trails of the Forest of Dean. Neil also talks to @greg_callaghan of @devinciglobalracing  before we find out about the design and development of the bike at Devinci Headquarters in Quebec, Canada.

node.title: First Look Event! The All-New Devinci Spartan | Lifting The Speed Bar

node.text: Welcome to the launch of the all new 2022 @cyclesdevinci Spartan enduro mountain bike! Watch now as @neildonoghue and @doddstar1979 check out all the details before taking it for a ride on the rough and fast trails of the Forest of Dean. Neil also talks to @greg_callaghan of @devinciglobalracing  before we find out about the design and development of the bike at Devinci Headquarters in Quebec, Canada.

node.text:
Two-stage wins in Loudenvielle and a 3rd in Crans Montana proves that @nogakorem is on pace! She's only 1 place away from equalling her @world_enduro career-best, and that means she's 2 away from the win! Is this the season?⁠
.⁠

node.text:
After hitting the road on Saturday's Pro Stage, @jackmoir_ took to Sunday's race with an injured shoulder hoping to mitigate his losses. That he did, finishing 10th on the day, leaving him at a 90 point deficit to @richie_rude1. It's all to play for in Finale. ⁠
.⁠
